 mean when we cross the $100 million mark, and we=E2=80=99re headed toward =
that this year. For that milestone, I do think it has motivated us to have =
conversations to potentially find the right partner. We=E2=80=99re really l=
ooking for someone who understands the brand vision [and] would prioritize =
long-term
healthy growth. We are open to the right partner for an initial minority in=
vestment, and because we are growing pretty quickly, we=E2=80=99re mindful =
of how that growth could make for a potentially more difficult transaction.=
 Historically, we=E2=80=99ve been profitable and we=E2=80=99re at the point=
 now where we=E2=80=99re having really healthy double-digit EBITDA.<br/><br=
/></p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Let=E2=80=99s talk a=
